OL,6,FAround 10 million pensioners are
OL,7,Fexpected to lose out on winter fuel
OL,8,Fpayments as a result of the policy,
OL,9,Fwhich the Government has revealed as
OL,10,Fpart of its plan to tackle a #22
OL,11,Fbillion "black hole".
