OL,16,Fthe previous governments means we are
OL,17,Fhaving to take tough decisions now to
OL,18,Ffix the foundations of our economy `
OL,19,Fincluding making the winter fuel
OL,20,Fpayments available to those most at
OL,21,Fneed.
